Package: darklyplot
Title: Make Simple Dark Themed Time Series Plots
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Leonard", "Kiefer", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "lenkiefer@hotmail.com")
Description: This packages lets you create simple dark-theme times series plots.  
    It extends ggplot2 and relies on mdthemes to make color coded axis labels.
    The axis labels use ggthemes::geom_rangeframe to create Tufte-like axes.
    Through parameters, the user can alter the colors, include shading under the line,
    and also add a single reference line.
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    dplyr,
    glue,
    ggplot2,
    ggthemes,
    mdthemes,
    scales,
    shiny
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
